snippet.title: Best VGM 1469 - The Last Story - Invitation to Madness
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 985 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-LLr-88UG1U

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii
The Last Story (2011)
Invitation to Madness
Nobuo Uematsu
